												<DIV>I use the Belkin Nostromo N52, I love it...&nbsp; I have severe pain in my left wrist (the one I use from twisting) and up the arm, I'm not blaming EQ, but it doesn't help..&nbsp; The Nostromo has been a GODSEND!!&nbsp; One thing that needs to change is the way songs start/stop...&nbsp; With my cleric I have a hotkey that looks similar to this</DIV>
