			<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; " >
												<P>I use a Nostromo n52 to play a Ranger, Warrior, and Cleric.&nbsp; I absolutely love it!&nbsp; I <STRONG>highly</STRONG> recommend it to <STRONG>all</STRONG> classes.&nbsp; I haven't programmed a profile for the n52 for my baby Bard (Level 26), but I'm sure it will work relatively well once I do.&nbsp; The <STRONG>only</STRONG> problem with the n52 is that it is really just a "Typing Assistant".&nbsp; Any commands you "program" in and have sent from one of the gamepad's keys is <STRONG>typed</STRONG> into your chat window.&nbsp; During archery auto-fire, if I try to chat, I get 1's inserted in all my conversation.</P>
<P>Th1at's sur1vivable th1ough as 1most peo1ple know1 what's g1oing on wh1en they see i1t!</P>
